spec_data.Name: mod_mono
spec_data.Description:
mod_mono allows Apache to serve ASP.NET pages by proxying the requests
to a slightly modified version of the XSP server, called mod-mono-server,
that is installed along with XSP
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 04 Aug 2017 06:05:06 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: A module to deploy an ASP.NET application on Apache with Mono
